1
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,580
=Reincarnated Love=

2
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:43,700
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:49,920
(Yanzhi,)

4
00:00:50,280 --> 00:00:51,430
(give me some time.)

5
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:52,960
(In this lifetime,)

6
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:55,110
(I will change everyone's fate.)

7
00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:57,320
Milady.

8
00:00:58,640 --> 00:00:59,480
Milady,

9
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:01,110
as you instructed,

10
00:01:01,110 --> 00:01:02,520
I investigated that shopkeeper.

11
00:01:03,020 --> 00:01:04,180
Just as you predicted,

12
00:01:04,630 --> 00:01:07,070
he's quite close to Master Huaikang.

13
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:12,540
(Ledger)

14
00:01:14,710 --> 00:01:15,710
(Jiang Huaikang,)

15
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:19,000
(your scheme will fail this time.)

16
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:28,680
Ruoli,

17
00:01:29,350 --> 00:01:31,000
why do you look so pale?

18
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,680
Has something happened?

19
00:01:34,710 --> 00:01:37,200
You teamed up with the shopkeeper
to frame my father

20
00:01:37,790 --> 00:01:39,680
and sow discord between officials.

21
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:43,070
Could it be you intend
to stir chaos in court?

22
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,120
Jiang Ruoli,

23
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,820
do you even know what you're saying?

24
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,680
Every deal between you

25
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:54,120
and the shopkeeper was recorded.

26
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,710
Since when did you

27
00:01:55,710 --> 00:01:57,680
grow so generous?

28
00:01:59,070 --> 00:02:00,230
Something's wrong!

29
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,840
Mr. Huo is here.

30
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:08,840
Jiang Ruoli,

31
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,686
the date we agreed upon has come.

32
00:02:11,150 --> 00:02:12,590
I'm here to see the evidence.

33
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,870
It was Jiang Huaikang.

34
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,430
The shop he oversees

35
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,360
accepted money of dubious origin.

36
00:02:20,793 --> 00:02:21,892
(Ledger)
This is the proof.

37
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,240
Be it Jiang Huaikang

38
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:32,870
or Jiang Huai'an,

39
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,150
it's still a Jiang.

40
00:02:36,310 --> 00:02:37,150
Jiang Ruoli,

41
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:38,870
I really underestimated you.

42
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,630
I didn't expect you to be so persuasive.

43
00:02:42,710 --> 00:02:46,710
Was the story made up
to save your father?

44
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:48,030
Jiang Huaikang,

45
00:02:49,310 --> 00:02:51,080
were you the one behind this?

46
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,560
Mr. Huo,

47
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,740
that shop indeed

48
00:02:56,310 --> 00:02:57,310
belongs to me.

49
00:02:57,820 --> 00:02:59,190
But I know nothing of this.

50
00:03:00,030 --> 00:03:00,910
It must be Huai'an.

51
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:03,560
Yes, he framed me on purpose.

52
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,750
He forced that trouble upon me

53
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:06,870
and made me take the blame.

54
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:09,310
Please see the truth, Mr. Huo.

55
00:03:09,630 --> 00:03:10,710
That's pure slander.

56
00:03:10,710 --> 00:03:11,550
Mr. Huo...

57
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,640
Jiang Ruoli,

58
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:19,240
do you really think I wouldn't kill you?

59
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,870
Hand over your father now.

60
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,640
Otherwise,

61
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:23,960
I'll wipe out

62
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,630
your entire family today.

63
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,960
Yanzhi,

64
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,630
it's not like that.

65
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:32,840
Who allowed you to call me that?

66
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:34,960
Tell me.

67
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:37,080
Where is your father?

68
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,030
Or I'll really do it.

69
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,000
Deputy Chen Guang

70
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:45,710
is still alive.

71
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,030
What?

72
00:03:48,310 --> 00:03:49,360
It's a secret.

73
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,360
How did you find out?

74
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:53,590
Yanzhi, stop!

75
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,240
What are you doing?

76
00:04:00,470 --> 00:04:01,360
Father was wronged.

77
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:02,630
I understand your impatience,

78
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,080
but you still can't

79
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:05,360
treat Yuan this way.

80
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,800
Huaijin,

81
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:10,590
you'd best stay out of this.

82
00:04:12,630 --> 00:04:13,710
Yunzhou.

83
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:16,000
Eunuch Wang is here.

84
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,800
His Majesty has issued a decree.

85
00:04:25,950 --> 00:04:28,360
Jiang Huaikang is accused
of embezzling military funds.

86
00:04:28,750 --> 00:04:30,310
Seize him at once!

87
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:31,960
Eunuch,

88
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:35,000
I've never touched military funds!

89
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:44,160
The evidence is undeniable.

90
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,560
Seize him

91
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:47,870
for a full investigation.

92
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,520
Eunuch!

93
00:04:49,950 --> 00:04:51,120
I'm innocent!

94
00:04:51,870 --> 00:04:52,920
What are you waiting for?

95
00:04:53,190 --> 00:04:54,430
Take him away.

96
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,190
I'm innocent!

97
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:58,390
Eunuch, I'm innocent!

98
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:00,360
I'm innocent!

99
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,600
I'm innocent!

100
00:05:01,750 --> 00:05:03,000
I'm innocent!

101
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:05,480
Please, everyone, rise.

102
00:05:11,630 --> 00:05:12,870
Mr. Huo,

103
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,360
what's happening?

104
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,430
Eunuch Wang,

105
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:18,600
I'm worried about my father,

106
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,070
so I came to investigate.

107
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:23,390
Your filial devotion is admirable.

108
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:27,360
The Duke didn't embezzle military funds,

109
00:05:28,190 --> 00:05:30,630
but the proof of treason...

110
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:33,120
Mr. Huo, don't worry.

111
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:35,390
His Majesty is having a full inquiry.

112
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:39,360
The truth will soon come to light.

113
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:42,920
Why was this case concluded so swiftly?

114
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:45,920
You may not know this.

115
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:49,600
Jiang Huaikang has made
many enemies within the court.

116
00:05:49,830 --> 00:05:52,040
Evidence against him had piled up high.

117
00:05:52,510 --> 00:05:54,480
Once His Majesty
ordered the investigation,

118
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,510
his guilt was confirmed at once.

119
00:05:57,950 --> 00:06:00,070
His Majesty also understands

120
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:03,800
that the Duke must've been wronged,

121
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:07,240
so I was sent to handle it asap.

122
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:11,993
How wise of His Majesty.

123
00:06:12,950 --> 00:06:14,020
Thank you for your trouble.

124
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,720
You're too polite.

125
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,720
If it's okay with you,

126
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:19,390
I'll take my leave now.

127
00:06:20,510 --> 00:06:21,430
Goodbye.

128
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,800
(Is Huo Linchuan recalling something?)

129
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,800
(Did I truly wrong her?)

130
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,630
(How could she know about Chen Guang?)

131
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:43,110
(Could it be her memory never faded?)

132
00:06:47,510 --> 00:06:48,430
Yuan,

133
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,630
are you okay?

134
00:06:49,950 --> 00:06:51,560
Yanzhi has always been stubborn.

135
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:54,630
Even nine oxen couldn't pull him back.

136
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:58,120
Besides,
this concerns his father's life.

137
00:06:58,830 --> 00:07:00,870
You mustn't take it to heart.

138
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:03,110
Yuan,

139
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:04,390
wipe your sweat.

140
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,440
Yuan,

141
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,440
are you all right?

142
00:07:27,630 --> 00:07:28,470
Yuan,

143
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:30,270
what's wrong?

144
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,070
You took it too seriously.

145
00:07:37,270 --> 00:07:38,110
I know.

146
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:39,750
Mr. Huo

147
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,560
is only worried about his father.

148
00:07:42,270 --> 00:07:43,190
I understand.

149
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:46,160
When you argued with Yanzhi,

150
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:48,430
I thought
I heard you mention Chen Guang.

151
00:07:49,310 --> 00:07:50,270
How did you know

152
00:07:50,270 --> 00:07:51,270
about that name?

153
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,950
From what I know,

154
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:56,560
he was the deputy
whom Father trusted most.

155
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:58,800
He always acted in secrecy.

156
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:01,070
Chen Guang?

157
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,120
You must've misheard.

158
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:07,120
I just heard the servants whispering

159
00:08:07,310 --> 00:08:09,310
that before Duke Huo's accident,

160
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:11,830
he'd grown close to General Chen.

161
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:15,070
Later, he vanished without a trace.

162
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,510
I was merely guessing at the time,

163
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:21,510
wondering if the two of them
were in league.

164
00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:22,950
So, I wanted Mr. Huo to look into it.

165
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:25,720
I never thought it would make him
so furious.

166
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:38,540
(Jiang Mansion)

167
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,800
Yuan,

168
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,550
your careful nature is commendable.

169
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:46,320
But matters of war and state
are too complex.

170
00:08:46,750 --> 00:08:48,440
You must speak with caution
in the future.

171
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:51,360
I'll explain things to Yanzhi for you.

172
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,960
Just go back and rest easy.

173
00:08:55,390 --> 00:08:56,870
Then I'll trouble you, Yunzhou.

174
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:58,270
I'll take my leave for now.

175
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,440
Sure.

176
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:06,790
Yuan, go inside.

177
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,680
Sure.

178
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:15,630
(Yuan,)

179
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,670
(you'd better not deceive me.)

180
00:09:27,790 --> 00:09:28,630
(Lu Huaijin,)

181
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:32,200
(your little test is far too clumsy.)

182
00:09:52,810 --> 00:09:54,330
♪The dream shattered♪

183
00:09:54,690 --> 00:09:56,370
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

184
00:09:56,370 --> 00:09:58,010
♪Like a restless soul♪

185
00:09:58,890 --> 00:10:00,450
♪How vague♪

186
00:10:00,850 --> 00:10:02,370
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

187
00:10:02,370 --> 00:10:04,610
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

188
00:10:05,410 --> 00:10:08,010
♪Love and hate entwined♪

189
00:10:08,490 --> 00:10:11,330
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

190
00:10:11,970 --> 00:10:16,730
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

191
00:10:17,330 --> 00:10:18,850
♪When fate falls apart♪

192
00:10:19,250 --> 00:10:22,810
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

193
00:10:23,530 --> 00:10:25,090
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

194
00:10:25,490 --> 00:10:29,210
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

195
00:10:29,930 --> 00:10:32,770
♪Life after life♪

196
00:10:33,250 --> 00:10:35,930
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

197
00:10:36,570 --> 00:10:40,650
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

198
00:10:40,730 --> 00:10:43,770
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

199
00:10:43,930 --> 00:10:45,330
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

200
00:10:45,330 --> 00:10:48,450
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

201
00:10:48,530 --> 00:10:49,970
♪Now shatter apart♪

202
00:10:50,090 --> 00:10:53,850
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

203
00:10:54,570 --> 00:10:57,370
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

204
00:10:57,650 --> 00:11:00,490
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

205
00:11:00,810 --> 00:11:05,210
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

206
00:11:05,450 --> 00:11:08,370
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

207
00:11:08,490 --> 00:11:12,930
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

208
00:11:13,130 --> 00:11:18,850
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

209
00:11:19,290 --> 00:11:22,010
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

210
00:11:22,250 --> 00:11:24,970
♪Sober or indulge♪

211
00:11:25,410 --> 00:11:31,410
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪
